\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
gls{saaf}
\end_layout

\end_inset

) form of the transport equation has been discretized using 
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
gls{cfem}
\end_layout

\end_inset

 and implemented with 
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
gls{supg}
\end_layout

\end_inset

 stabilization 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "wang-nonlinear-2013"
literal "true"

\end_inset

