 The inverse of the total cross section is used as the 
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
gls{supg}
\end_layout

\end_inset

 stabilization parameter (see Sec.
 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "subsec:supg-stabilization"

\end_inset

