 Near void regions, a characteristic distance for each element is used,
 which is similar to the treatment of the 
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
gls{supg}
\end_layout

\end_inset

 parameter in Sec.
 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
