\end{align}

\end_inset


\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
end{subequations}
\end_layout

\end_inset

The basis-weighted operators have the superscript 
\begin_inset Formula $b$
\end_inset

.
 The source and reflection operators are unchanged from Eq.
 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:full-transport"

\end_inset

.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
In addition to preserving particle balance as discussed in Sec.
 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "subsec:particle-balance"

\end_inset

, the 
