status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
gls{supg}
\end_layout

\end_inset

 stabilization also allows the cross sections to be integrated without direction
al dependence.
 If the weight functions were instead skewed or offset in the upwind direction,
 these integrals cross sections would additionally be dependent on the direction
 
