\end_inset

 code with 500000 elements and linear basis and weight functions within
 each element.
 The average solution 
\begin_inset Formula $\bar{\phi}_{i,g}^{\text{bench}}$
\end_inset

 over 1000 overlaid cells with index 
\begin_inset Formula $i$
\end_inset

 for each energy group 
\begin_inset Formula $g$
\end_inset

 is then calculated.
 After completion of the 
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
gls{mlpg}
\end_layout

\end_inset

 solution, the average scalar flux 
\begin_inset Formula $\bar{\phi}_{i,g}$
\end_inset

