\begin_inset Formula $r_{1,\pm}=r_{b}\pm\Delta r_{min}/2$
\end_inset

, where 
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta r_{min}$
\end_inset

 is the desired minimum spacing between points in the problem.
 Further rings of points are added at 
\begin_inset Formula $r_{n,\pm}=r_{n-1,\pm}\pm t^{n-1}\Delta r_{min}$
\end_inset

